    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nWhen importing `pyximport`, the following deprecation warning occurs.\r\n\r\n```\r\npyximport/pyximport.py:51: DeprecationWarning: the imp module is deprecated in favour of importlib; see the module's documentation for alternative uses\r\nimport imp\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis warning is equivalent to the one reported in #3306 and can be traced back to this line\r\nhttps://github.com/cython/cython/blob/master/pyximport/pyximport.py#L51\r\n\r\n```cython\r\nimport pyximport\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nA similar replacement of `import imp` as in this PR https://github.com/cython/cython/pull/3350/commits/be284d62bc9fdff691530e0d9a9bb40a93941464 could be employed\r\n\r\n",
